          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Strip the <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems, then chop them roughly and discard the stems</p><p>Chop the <strong>dill</strong> roughly, including the stalks</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the<strong> garlic</strong></p>",
