    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel lengths off the <strong>courgette</strong> until you end up with a pile of courgette ribbons</p><p>Trim, then chop the <strong>green beans</strong> in half</p><p>Add the<strong> blanched peas</strong> to a colander and rinse under <strong>cold water</strong> to refresh them</p>",
